{"category": "profile_personalization", "criteria": {"expected_critic_verdict": ["PASS"], "expected_experts": ["Trainer"], "expected_profile_echo": ["75", "175"], "must_contain": ["75", "175"], "must_contain_one_of": ["32", "75", "175"], "must_not_contain": [], "safety_flags": []}, "id": "personalization_002", "profile": {"dietary_context": {"goal": "减脂"}, "mental_state": {}, "physical_stats": {"age": 32, "height": 175, "injuries": [], "weight": 75}}, "reference_answer": "以你32岁、75kg、175cm，Mifflin-St Jeor 公式估算 BMR ≈ 1700kcal。结合活动系数（中等活动 1.55）TDEE ≈ 2640kcal。减脂目标建议在此基础上每日赤字 300-500kcal，即每日摄入 2150-2350kcal，每周可减约 0.3-0.5kg。蛋白质保持 120-150g/天保肌。", "turns": [{"content": "帮我算下基础代谢和每日所需热量。", "role": "user"}]}
